		    <div class="title"><h1><a href="/pages/blackberry-internet-service/">BlackBerry Internet Service</a></h1></div>
		    <p>My notes on using <a href="http://www.blackberry.com/support/client/index.shtml">BlackBerry Internet Service</a> with or without a BES
account</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="/2006/08/11/using-bis-with-bes/">Using BIS with BES</a></li>
<li><a href="/2006/12/21/why-is-bis-with-bes-hidden-so-well/">Why is BIS with BES Hidden so Well?</a></li>
<li><a href="/2006/12/14/a-bit-more-bis-blackberry-and-imap/">A bit more BIS: BlackBerry and IMAP</a></li>
</ul>


<h3>Access to BIS</h3>

<ul>
<li>DE

<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.mobileemail.vodafone.de">Vodafone</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.instantemail.t-mobile.de/">T-Mobile</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.eplus.blackberry.com/">E Plus</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.o2.blackberry.de/">O2</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>UK

<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.o2email.co.uk">O2</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>US

<ul>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=DobsonCellular">Dobson</a></li>
<li><a href="http://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=earthlink">Earthlink Wireless</a></li>
<li><a href="http://ntelos.blackberry.com/">NTELOS</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=nextel">Nextel</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=rogers">Rogers Wireless</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=sprint">Sprint</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=Mobility">Mobility</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.alltel.blackberry.com/">Alltel</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=bell">Bell Mobility</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=CellularOne">CellularOne</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=csouth1">Cellular South</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=cinbell">Cincinnati Bell</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.cingular.com/blackberrystart">Cingular Wireless</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=suncom">SunCom</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=tmo">T-Mobile</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=tcs">TeleCommunication Systems</a></li>
<li><a href="https://webclient.blackberry.net/WebMail/Window.jsp?site=telus">TELUS Mobility</a></li>
